sql:
SELECT last_download_date 
FROM componentDownloads 
WHERE component_id = 'specific_component_id';

SELECT component_id, tag_name
FROM componentTags
WHERE component_id = 'your_component_id_here';

SELECT component_id, COUNT(doc_id) 
FROM componentDocumentation
GROUP BY component_id;

external_knowledge:
- "vibrant elements of the digital garden" metaphorically refers to active GUI components;
- "currently blooming" metaphorically refers to components that are active (is_active = 1);
- "unique gardeners" metaphorically refers to distinct developer IDs associated with each component.

sql:
SELECT MAX(is_active) AS max_active_status
FROM gui_components
WHERE is_active = 1;

SELECT gui_components.component_id, gui_components.class_name, componentLicenses.license_type
FROM gui_components
JOIN componentLicenses ON gui_components.component_id = componentLicenses.component_id;

SELECT feature_name, description, default_value 
FROM componentFeatures 
WHERE component_id = 123;

external_knowledge:
- The term 'primary component' refers to the component with `component_id` = 1 in the GUI; 
- 'Type' corresponds to the class name of the component; 
- 'Identifier' refers to the reference name, which uniquely labels the component within its context.

sql:
SELECT class_name, reference
FROM gui_components
WHERE component_id = 1;
